goals.rationale: This visualization will help us identify which genus of bacteria is most susceptible to the antibiotics and which antibiotic is most effective against each genus.

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['Penicillin'], bins=11, color='green', alpha=0.75)
    plt.axvline(data['Penicillin'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean')
    plt.axvline(data['Penicillin'].median(), color='blue', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median')
    plt.legend()
    plt.xlabel('Penicillin Effectiveness')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Penicillin effectiveness against the different bacteria species?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.boxplot([data['Streptomycin'], data['Penicillin'], data['Neomycin']])
    ax.set_xticklabels(['Streptomycin', 'Penicillin', 'Neomycin'])
    ax.set_ylabel('Effectiveness')
    ax.set_title('How does the effectiveness of Streptomycin compare to that of Penicillin and Neomycin?')
    plt.show()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Gram_Staining'] = data['Gram_Staining'].astype('category')
    data['Penicillin'] = pd.to_numeric(data['Penicillin'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['Penicillin'])
    data = data[['Gram_Staining', 'Penicillin']]
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.boxplot([data[data['Gram_Staining'] == 'positive']['Penicillin'], data[data['Gram_Staining'] == 'negative']['Penicillin']], labels=['Gram-positive', 'Gram-negative'])
    ax.set_ylabel('Penicillin effectiveness')
    ax.set_title('How does the effectiveness of Penicillin vary between Gram-positive and Gram-negative bacteria?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data.groupby(['Genus']).mean()
    data = data[['Penicillin', 'Streptomycin', 'Neomycin']]
    ax = data.plot(kind='bar', rot=0)
    ax.set_xlabel('Genus')
    ax.set_ylabel('Mean effectiveness')
    ax.set_title('Which genus of bacteria is most susceptible to the antibiotics?')
    ax.legend(title='Antibiotic', loc='upper left')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
